  "texts": [
    "Similarly, classification tasks can be tackled using either machine learning or deep learning.",
    "It is widely acknowledged that deep learning algorithms outperform machine learning when provided with extensive datasets.",
    "Advanced augmentation techniques have expanded the horizons, making dataset size less of an obstacle.",
    "Section 4 outlines some of the deep learning techniques.",
    "Refinement and validation take centre stage."
